title: 14YA | Masters of the Majors
body_text:
It's takes one hell of an effort to stand tall at the end of an ECD Major event. And as you would expect, the most recognized names in the game almost always come out on top. NOTE: Every name listed in the infographic is an ECDElite Hall of Famer.
Who will grab hold the coveted 14YA trophy on August 17? Be there live, in person, to find out.
